cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.CL 

This paper proposes a new approach for semi-supervised learning under the multi-view scenario, which integrates manifold regularization and multi-view regularization into the usual formulation of SVMs. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
